{"id":"guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants","title":"Import global variants of the locale data","contents":"\n\n\n<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"import-global-variants-of-the-locale-data\" translation-result=\"on\">匯入語言環境資料的全域變體<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants#import-global-variants-of-the-locale-data\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1><h1 translation-origin=\"off\">Import global variants of the locale data<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants#import-global-variants-of-the-locale-data\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">如果你使用 <code>--localize</code> 選項執行 <a href=\"cli/build\" title=\"ng build | CLI | Angular\"><code>ng build</code></a> 命令，則 <a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> 會自動包含語言環境資料。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The <a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> automatically includes locale data if you run the <a href=\"cli/build\" title=\"ng build | CLI | Angular\"><code>ng build</code></a> command with the <code>--localize</code> option.</p>\n\n<!--todo: replace with code-example -->\n<code-example format=\"shell\" language=\"shell\">\n\nng build --localize\n\n</code-example>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">npm 上的 <code>@angular/common</code> 套件中包含語言環境資料檔案。語言環境資料的全域變體來自 <a href=\"https://unpkg.com/browse/@angular/common/locales/global\" title=\"@angular/common/locales/global | Unpkg\"><code>@angular/common/locales/global</code></a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The <code>@angular/common</code> package on npm contains the locale data files.\nGlobal variants of the locale data are available in <a href=\"https://unpkg.com/browse/@angular/common/locales/global\" title=\"@angular/common/locales/global | Unpkg\"><code>@angular/common/locales/global</code></a>.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"import-example-for-french\" translation-result=\"on\">法語的 <code>import</code> 範例<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants#import-example-for-french\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\"><code>import</code> example for French<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants#import-example-for-french\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">以下範例匯入了法語（<code>fr</code>）的全域變體。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The following example imports the global variants for French (<code>fr</code>).</p>\n\n<code-example header=\"src/app/app.module.ts\" path=\"i18n/doc-files/app.module.ts\" region=\"global-locale\">\nimport '@angular/common/locales/<a href=\"api/core/global\" class=\"code-anchor\">global</a>/fr';\n\n</code-example>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最後複查時間：2/28/2022</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - guide/i18n-optional-overview\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/core/global\n - cli\n - cli/build\n - guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants#import-example-for-french\n - guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants#import-global-variants-of-the-locale-data\n - guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants#匯入語言環境資料的全域變體\n - guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants#法語的-import-範例\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\n - https://unpkg.com/browse/@angular/common/locales/global\n-->"}